</span>
<p style="background-position: 0% 0%; text-align: justify; color: #222222; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 1.44px; white-space: normal; text-shadow: none; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-repeat: repeat; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="background-position: 0% 0%; font-weight: 700; text-shadow: none; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-repeat: repeat; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; color: #006600;"></span></p>
