<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: large; word-spacing: 0.125em;"><span style="line-height: 1.25;"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px;">VOTER FORMS</span></strong>:</span></strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
    <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="line-height: 1.25; font-size: 16px;"><a href="https://www.ecp.gov.pk/documents/generalelections2018/voterforms/Form21.pdf">Form -21</a>&nbsp;(For enrollment / transfer of vote)</span></li>
    <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="line-height: 1.25; font-size: 16px;"><a href="https://www.ecp.gov.pk/documents/generalelections2018/voterforms/Form22.pdf">Form- 22</a>&nbsp;(For objection / deletion of vote)</span></li>
    <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="line-height: 1.25; font-size: 16px;"><a href="https://www.ecp.gov.pk/documents/generalelections2018/voterforms/Form23.pdf">Form- 23</a>&nbsp;(For correction of particulars)</span></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.25; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 75%; word-spacing: 0.12em;"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; color: #006600;">ELIGIBILITY TO BE A VOTER</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentcolor; text-align: justify; color: #5c5a52; text-transform: none; line-height: 19.5px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 13px;">A person shall be entitled to be enrolled as a voter in an electoral area if he&mdash; </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentcolor; text-align: justify; color: #5c5a52; text-transform: none; line-height: 19.5px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 13px;"> (a) is a citizen of Pakistan; </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentcolor; text-align: justify; color: #5c5a52; text-transform: none; line-height: 19.5px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 13px;"> (b) is not less than eighteen years of age; </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentcolor; text-align: justify; color: #5c5a52; text-transform: none; line-height: 19.5px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 13px;"> (c) possesses a National Identity Card issued by the National Database and Registration Authority at any time till the last day fixed for inviting claims, objections and applications for preparation, revision or correction of electoral rolls; </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentcolor; text-align: justify; color: #5c5a52; text-transform: none; line-height: 19.5px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 13px;">(d) is not declared by a competent court to be of unsound mind; and</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentcolor; text-align: justify; color: #5c5a52; text-transform: none; line-height: 19.5px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 13px;"> (e) is or is deemed under section 27 to be resident in the electoral area. </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentcolor; text-align: justify; color: #5c5a52; text-transform: none; line-height: 19.5px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 13px;">Explanation.&mdash;The National Identity Card issued by the National Database and Registration Authority shall be deemed to be valid for the purpose of registration as a voter or for casting vote in an election, notwithstanding the expiry of its validity period.&nbsp;</span></p></span>
